  <brief_title>Mercury II - Compare the Efficacy and Safety of Lipid Lowering Agents Atorvastatin and Simvastatin With Rosuvastatin in High Risk Subjects With Type IIa and IIb Hypercholesterolemia</brief_title>
  <official_title>An Open Label, Randomized, Multi-Center, Phase IIIB, Parallel Group Switching Study to Compare the Efficacy and Safety of Lipid Lowering Agents Atorvastatin and Simvastatin With Rosuvastatin in High Risk Subjects With Type IIa and IIb Hypercholesterolemia.</official_title>
